Own Choice Test Piece Contest
Cannock, Staffordshire Best cornet - Blakenhall Heath. Best horn - Dudley Town. According to British Bandsman p610 5/9/1903 - 7 bands competed. "No 8 Tutbury Town - unable to play; darkness coming on. The weather got worse and worse, and the contest finished in a fearful storm of wind and rain."
